attributeSource.infoString2: Wine Country Group BHG - Santa Rosa

data.description: Beautiful Fountaingrove Southridge home on rare, oversized lot of .4109 acre. Magnificent Redwood trees grace this backyard with a variety of other landscaping & fruit bearing trees. Spacious Living & Family room with vaulted ceilings & formal dining, hardwood flooring, tile bathrooms & two gas fireplaces, additional room for office, library or playroom, laundry room with deep sink & Three car garage. All New in 2018; 50yr re-roof with architectural roofing, HVAC, new appliances with gas cooktop & granite island, central vac, custom interior and exterior painting.  This cheerful home is like new and ready for the next owners to make it their own.  Meander through the .41 acre lot that feels like your enchanted oasis. One of each, Apple, Fig, Pomegranate, Lemon & Lime trees..... Producing and ready for your next harvest.  Primary bedroom has private deck over looking tranquil yard, two guest bedrooms and large office that can be used as 4th bedroom.
